extends ../_template

block vars

block content

  .wrapper
    +header
    .container
      div(role="alert" style={
        'background-color': styles.alert_color,
        'color': styles.alert_text_color
      }).alert.alert-warning.alert-dismissible
        button(type="button" data-dismiss="alert").close
          span(aria-hidden="true") &times;
          span.sr-only Close
        | This section contains a wealth of information, related to <strong>PrepBootstrap</strong> and its store. If you cannot find an answer to your question,
        | make sure to contact us.
      div(id="accordion").panel-group
        .faqHeader General questions
        .panel.panel-default
          div(role="tab").panel-heading
            h7.panel-title
              a(data-parent="#accordion" data-toggle="collapse" href="#collapseOne") Is account registration required?
          div(id="collapseOne").panel-collapse.collapse.in
            div(role="tabpanel").panel-body
              | Account registration at <strong>PrepBootstrap</strong> is only required if you will be selling or buying themes.
              | This ensures a valid communication channel for all parties involved in any transactions.
        .panel.panel-default
          div(role="tab").panel-heading
            h7.panel-title
              a(data-parent="#accordion" data-toggle="collapse" href="#collapseSecond") Can I submit my own Bootstrap templates or themes?
          div(id="collapseSecond").panel-collapse.collapse
            div(role="tabpanel").panel-body
              | A lot of the content of the site has been submitted by the community. Whether it is a commercial element/template/theme
              | or a free one, you are encouraged to contribute. All credits are published along with the resources.
        .panel.panel-default
          div(role="tab").panel-heading
            h7.panel-title
              a(data-parent="#accordion" data-toggle="collapse" href="#collapseThird") What is the currency used for all transactions?
          div(id="collapseThird").panel-collapse.collapse
            div(role="tabpanel").panel-body
              | All prices for themes, templates and other items, including each seller's or buyer's account balance are in <strong>USD</strong>
        .faqHeader Sellers
        .panel.panel-default
          div(role="tab").panel-heading
            h7.panel-title
              a(data-parent="#accordion" data-toggle="collapse" href="#collapseFour") Who cen sell items?
          div(id="collapseFour").panel-collapse.collapse
            div(role="tabpanel").panel-body
              | Any registed user, who presents a work, which is genuine and appealing, can post it on <strong>PrepBootstrap</strong>.
        .panel.panel-default
          div(role="tab").panel-heading
            h7.panel-title
              a(data-parent="#accordion" data-toggle="collapse" href="#collapseFifth") I want to sell my items - what are the steps?
          div(id="collapseFifth").panel-collapse.collapse
            div(role="tabpanel").panel-body
              | The steps involved in this process are really simple. All you need to do is:
              ul.casual-list
                li Register an account
                li Activate your account
                li
                  | Go to the <strong>Themes</strong> section and upload your theme
                li The next step is the approval step, which usually takes about 72 hours.
        .panel.panel-default
          div(role="tab").panel-heading
            h7.panel-title
              a(data-parent="#accordion" data-toggle="collapse" href="#collapseSix") How much do I get from each sale?
          div(id="collapseSix").panel-collapse.collapse
            div(role="tabpanel").panel-body
              | Here, at <strong>PrepBootstrap</strong>, we offer a great, 70% rate for each seller, regardless of any restrictions, such as volume, date of entry, etc.
        .panel.panel-default
          div(role="tab").panel-heading
            h7.panel-title
              a(data-parent="#accordion" data-toggle="collapse" href="#collapseSeventh") Why sell my items here?
          div(id="collapseSeventh").panel-collapse.collapse
            div(role="tabpanel").panel-body
              | There are a number of reasons why you should join us:
              ul.casual-list
                li A great 70% flat rate for your items.
                li Fast response/approval times. Many sites take weeks to process a theme or template. And if it gets rejected, there is another iteration. We have aliminated this, and made the process very fast. It only takes up to 72 hours for a template/theme to get reviewed.
                li We are not an exclusive marketplace. This means that you can sell your items on <strong>PrepBootstrap</strong>, as well as on any other marketplate, and thus increase your earning potential.
        .panel.panel-default
          div(role="tab").panel-heading
            h7.panel-title
              a(data-parent="#accordion" data-toggle="collapse" href="#collapseEight") What are the payment options?
          div(id="collapseEight").panel-collapse.collapse
            div(role="tabpanel").panel-body
              | The best way to transfer funds is via Paypal. This secure platform ensures timely payments and a secure environment.
        .panel.panel-default
          div(role="tab").panel-heading
            h7.panel-title
              a(data-parent="#accordion" data-toggle="collapse" href="#collapseNinth") When do I get paid?
          div(id="collapseNinth").panel-collapse.collapse
            div(role="tabpanel").panel-body
              | Our standard payment plan provides for monthly payments. At the end of each month, all accumulated funds are transfered to your account.
              | The minimum amount of your balance should be at least 70 USD.
        .faqHeader Buyers
        .panel.panel-default
          div(role="tab").panel-heading
            h7.panel-title
              a(data-parent="#accordion" data-toggle="collapse" href="#collapseTen") I want to buy a theme - what are the steps?
          div(id="collapseTen").panel-collapse.collapse
            div(role="tabpanel").panel-body
              | Buying a theme on <strong>PrepBootstrap</strong> is really simple. Each theme has a live preview.
              | Once you have selected a theme or template, which is to your liking, you can quickly and securely pay via Paypal.
              br
              | Once the transaction is complete, you gain full access to the purchased product.
        .panel.panel-default
          div(role="tab").panel-heading
            h7.panel-title
              a(data-parent="#accordion" data-toggle="collapse" href="#collapseEleven") Is this the latest version of an item
          div(id="collapseEleven").panel-collapse.collapse
            div(role="tabpanel").panel-body
              | Each item in <strong>PrepBootstrap</strong> is maintained to its latest version. This ensures its smooth operation.

    +footer
